# Implementation Plan: The Makhana House Website

This plan details the implementation of a professional, premium B2B and B2C website for "The Makhana House." We will use vanilla web technology (HTML5, CSS3, ES6 JavaScript) to ensure high performance, total design control, and SEO optimization.

## User Review Required

> [!CAUTION]
> The single-page website architecture is proposed for smoother transitions and a premium feel, avoiding page load interruptions while still serving all 4 requested pages as scrollable sections. Please review if you prefer strict multi-page loading instead of a smooth-scroll single page.

